&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Evaluate emerging AI/ML trends and apply them to enable transformative infrastructure automation solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
