&lt;li&gt;Deep experience with Git, pull request and code reviews as well as Jira for software development lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to operate in a fast-paced, deadline-driven, collaborative and iterative development environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to lead and define cloud initiatives and distill technical requirements from high-level product use cases to production-ready implementations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience establishing, promoting and ensuring best practices in cloud codebases including common architectures and standardized unit testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building reusable libraries, SDK’s and shared components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intricate knowledge of building and managing web services using REST and OpenAPI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS/MS in Computer Science or equivalent practical experience&lt;/li&gt;
