&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using AI tools to improve productivity, code quality, test quality, and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with embedded hardware devices&lt;/li&gt;
