&lt;li&gt;Strong, hands-on experience with the Yocto Project / OpenEmbedded, particularly maintaining and extending existing distributions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with BSPs, including bootloaders (e.g., U-Boot), Linux kernel configuration, and device trees.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in C/C++ for low-level and system software development.&lt;/li&gt;
