&lt;li&gt;Experience with hardware interfaces such as I2C, SPI, UART, GPIO, and USB.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with Git, CI/CD pipelines, and collaborative development workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working in a startup environment with evolving requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills and a collaborative mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
